{"tid":305343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我死左之後。。。","createTime":"2017-07-01T14:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T15:33:15.000Z","uid":68318,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"991624c2d6ec1845e072f5a88645c53b1177ac9a","tid":305343,"uid":68318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"屌。。好撚灰<br />\n無論係番工定番學果時<br />\n成日都係有想死既念頭係度<br />\n唔知點解就會覺得啲fd背住我攪啲野又唔話比我知<br />\n跟住就有種感覺係我死左反而佢地會開心啲<br />\n舉個例子先，<br />\n我前幾日同啲fd上另外一個fd屋企玩<br />\n總共係3男1女啦(識左6,7年)<br />\n跟住玩左個幾鍾之後<br />\n我要番工所以剩返2男1女係果度<br />\n一開頭覺得冇野既<br />\n跟住番工放break果陣wts佢地<br />\n但係佢地全部都冇應機<br />\n攪<br />\n因為我本身對條女都有好感既<br />\n攪到我開始覺得會唔會係佢地係度3p定迷姦左條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到我超灰<br />\n開始覺得因為係我唔夠佢地咁有錢定型(中上樣)而無能為力<br />\n覺得死左都冇人會為我傷心同埋死左都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到番完工之後<br />\n佢地先wts番我(條女冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n佢地都係話我走左之後係度打機<br />\n<br />\n我想問巴絲打，我應唔應該信佢地。。。<br />\n同埋我死左係咪真係我諗既咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 and 長文<br />\n利申 19歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc8c54cfccb7abf0893b3b731ceb4ff264b2528","tid":305343,"uid":68318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9820d0e1aebca28bf1f04f07f882421f728b955","tid":305343,"uid":68318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d85ccec24ef0e966127665ac62abc94d9f23b6","tid":305343,"uid":68318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4cc65688ac44239a8f09faada07af7d1a586d6","tid":3